Package: udp-filter
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libgeoip1 (>= 1.4.6)
Description: <Wikimedia's udp-filter system.>
 WMF logs pageviews by listing to the udp2log daemon. udp-filter allows
 you to configure a filter and write particular pageviews, based on a
 combination of domain and url matching, to a logfile. It also offers
 geocoding, anonymization and ip-range filtering of ip addresses.
